summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Seattle Center Department; authorizing execution of a Memorandum of Agreement with the Seattle Symphony that makes various City commitments with respect to the official name for the new concert hall proposed for the block bounded by Mercer and Roy Streets and Second and Third Avenues, provides consulting opportunities to the Benaroya Foundation regarding the planning and construction of such facility, and establishes an agreed-upon date for commencement of construction.
